{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"getter"},{"kind":"text","text":"="},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isDraggable"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If this property is set to "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the user can drag the annotation after"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pressing and holding the view, and the associated annotation object must also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implement the "},{"code":"setCoordinate:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method. The default value of this property is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" lets the map view know that the annotation is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"always draggable. In other words, you cannot conditionalize drag operations by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attempting to stop an operation that has already been initiated; doing so can","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"lead to undefined behavior. Once begun, the drag operation should always","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"continue to completion.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","level":4,"anchor":"Related-examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Enable users to drag "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" objects on your map."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L261"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)draggable","title":"draggable","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/draggable":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"}],"role":"symbol","title":"draggable","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable"}}}